txt.en: You have stood defiantly against the servants of Sauron and you have devastated the armies of the Enemy in defence of Caras Gelebren.
Before Celebrimbor and the last of the Elves fell defeated and Eregion was laid waste, countless enemies loyal to Sauron met their doom at Caras Gelebren.
Defeat the servants of Sauron at Caras Gelebren
